transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan, iktha ji.
Customer: Haan, sir bataye.
Customer: Haan, Tulesh Nasri se baat kar raha hu.
Executive: Sir, mujhe ek minute dijiye, mai iktha se call back kara dunga.
Customer: Haan, suniye na, mera jo ye jo buylead dikhta hai, ye check karo recent buylead options.
Customer: Select karke wo bhi check karo, to 5-6 ghanta purana purana lead sab dikhai de rahi hai.
Customer: Ek bar dekh lijiye.
Executive: Latest buylead nahi aa rahi hai.
Customer: Recent buylead jis time check kar raha hu na, all over India karke recent karke, to matlab 6 ghanta, 20 ghante is type purana purana lead dikhai de rahi hai.
Executive: Achha.
Customer: Matlab ye to hona chahiye je 20 minute pahle lead post hua, wo dikh rahi hai, is type nahi hota hai. Kya ho gaya ek bar dekh lijiye.
Executive: Hmm.
Executive: Ek minute mai iktha se call back kara rahi hu sir, ek minute dijiyega.
Customer: Thik hai, thik hai.
summary:

- Old buyleads are being displayed.

- Wants recent buyleads to be displayed.
